<doc id="42323" wikidata="Q348380" url="?curid=42323" title="Lincoln Park (disambiguation)">
<text>[[Lincoln Park]] is an urban park in Chicago, which gave its name to the Lincoln Park, Chicago community area.

Lincoln Park may also refer to:
